"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?36/9/37015/contributors\">",
"     Kent L Christopher, MD, RRT, FCCP, FAARC",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"   </div>",
"   <div>",
